<h2 class="bold font-l">Miss Hattie</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Miss Hattie, owner of Miss Hattie's Home for Girls, mistreats the orphaned girls and forces them to sell cookies to make profit. Anyone who disobeys her will be sent to the &quot;Box of Shame&quot;. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
